<p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  The following reimbursement <%= @expenses.one? ? "claim is" : "claims are" %> charged to a budget
  you own and <%= @expenses.one? ? "needs" : "need" %> your sign-off before the finance team can pay
  <%= @expenses.one? ? "it" : "them" %>:
</p>

<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;">Claim</th>
      <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;">Budget</th>
      <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;">Payee</th>
      <th style="text-align: right; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;">Amount</th>
      <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;">Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <% @expenses.each do |expense| %>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;">#<%= expense.auto_number %></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><%= expense.budget&.name %></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><%= expense.effective_payee_name %></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6; text-align: right;"><%= number_to_currency(expense.amount, unit: "£") %></td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><%= expense.description %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><%= link_to "Review and endorse on My Budgets", admin_reimbursements_my_budgets_url %></p>

<p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 0.9em;">
  You're getting this because you own the budget. Any one owner can endorse, and each claim clears
  as soon as one of you does. You'll get this daily until they're all resolved.
</p>

<p>Regards,</p>

<p>Pineapple</p>
